    <title>数据结构</title>
    <link href="/2024/03/23/review/"/>
    <url>/2024/03/23/review/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="数据结构"><a href="#数据结构" class="headerlink" title="数据结构"></a>数据结构</h2><h3 id="渐进分析与算法复杂度分析"><a href="#渐进分析与算法复杂度分析" class="headerlink" title="渐进分析与算法复杂度分析"></a>渐进分析与算法复杂度分析</h3><ul><li>Big-O：$f(n) &#x3D; O(g(n))$<ul><li>$f(n)$ 的增长速度不大于$g(n)$：$\lim_{n \to \infty}\frac{f(n)}{g(n)} &#x3D; c, c \in[0, \infty)$</li></ul></li><li>Little-O: $f(n) &#x3D; o(g(n))$<ul><li>$f(n)$ 的增长速度小于$g(n)$：$\lim_{n \to \infty}\frac{f(n)}{g(n)} &#x3D; 0$</li></ul></li><li>Big-Theta：$f(n) &#x3D; \Theta(g(n))$<ul><li>$f(n)$ 的增长速度等同于$g(n)$：$\lim_{n \to \infty}\frac{f(n)}{g(n)} &#x3D; c, c \in(0, \infty)$</li></ul></li><li>Big-Omega：$f(n) &#x3D; \Omega(g(n))$<ul><li>$f(n)$ 的增长速度不小于$g(n)$：$\lim_{n \to \infty}\frac{f(n)}{g(n)} &#x3D; c, c \in(0, \infty]$</li></ul></li><li>Little-Omega：$f(n) &#x3D; \omega(g(n))$<ul><li>$f(n)$ 的增长速度大于$g(n)$：$\lim_{n \to \infty}\frac{f(n)}{g(n)} &#x3D; \infty$</li></ul></li><li>递归分析：主定理 <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Master_theorem_(analysis_of_algorithms)">Master Theorem</a></li></ul><h3 id="链表、栈、队列"><a href="#链表、栈、队列" class="headerlink" title="链表、栈、队列"></a>链表、栈、队列</h3><ul><li>栈应用：括号匹配，深度搜索</li><li>队列应用：广度搜索</li></ul><h3 id="串"><a href="#串" class="headerlink" title="串"></a>串</h3><ul><li>字符串匹配<ul><li>Brute-Force：O(mn)</li><li>KMP: O(m+n)</li></ul></li><li></li></ul><h3 id="树"><a href="#树" class="headerlink" title="树"></a>树</h3><ul><li>基本概念<ul><li>树：无重复边和自环，分为内部节点和叶子节点。</li><li>树的节点的度、树的度、树的节点的深度、树的深度</li><li>m 元树、正则 m 元树（full m-ary tree）、二叉树（二元有根有序树）</li><li>平衡树：叶子节点深度为树高度或树高度减一（不严谨）</li></ul></li><li>树的定理<ul><li>n 个节点有 n-1 条边</li><li>正则 m 元树有 k 个内部节点，则有 mk+1 个节点</li><li>对于一个正则 m 元树，n 个节点，k 个内部节点，l 个叶子，有<ul><li>k&#x3D;(n−1)&#x2F;m,l&#x3D;[(m−1)n+1]&#x2F;m</li><li>n&#x3D;mk+1,l&#x3D;(m−1)k+1</li><li>n&#x3D;(ml−1)&#x2F;(m−1), k&#x3D;(l−1)&#x2F;(m−1)</li></ul></li><li>高度为 h 的 m 元树最多有 $m^h$ 叶子</li><li>如果一个高度为 h 的 m 元树有 l 叶子，则 h &gt;&#x3D; $log_m l$</li></ul></li><li>Parental Tree（结点指向父亲），采用数组即可实现<br>  <img src="/review/ParentalTree.jpg"></li><li>二叉树<ul><li>概念<ul><li>正则二叉树(full binary trees)：内部节点度数都为2</li><li>完美二叉树&#x2F;满二叉树(perfect binary trees)：所有叶子结点同高度，所有内部节点都有两个孩子结点<ul><li>高度 h 的满二叉树有 $2^{h+1}-1$ 节点</li><li>高度 h 的满二叉树有 $2^h$ 叶子节点</li></ul></li><li>完全二叉树(complete binary trees)：从左到右填满对应高度的完美二叉树，最后一层允许不满<ul><li>n 个节点的完全二叉树的高度为 h &#x3D; $\lfloor log_2 n \rfloor$</li><li>完全二叉树适合使用数组存储，首位不使用，存储顺序与广搜一致。结点k的儿子结点为 2k(k&lt;&lt;1) 和 2k+1 (左儿子结点|1)，父亲结点为 k&#x2F;2(k&gt;&gt;1);</li></ul></li><li>平衡二叉树：Height balancing(AVL)，Null-path-length balancing(Red-black trees)，Weight balancing(Boundedbalance trees)</li></ul></li><li>遍历：前序、中序、后序遍历</li><li>实现：  <figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-string">&lt;algorithm&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Binary_node</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">protected</span>:<br>    Type node_value;<br>    Binary_node *p_left_tree;<br>    Binary_node *p_right_tree;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">Binary_node</span>(Type <span class="hljs-type">const</span> &amp;);<br>    <span class="hljs-function">Type <span class="hljs-title">value</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-type">const</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">Binary_node *<span class="hljs-title">left</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-type">const</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">Binary_node *<span class="hljs-title">right</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-type">const</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title">is_leaf</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-type">const</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">size</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-type">const</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">height</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> <span class="hljs-type">const</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">clear</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br>Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;::<span class="hljs-built_in">Binary_node</span>(Type <span class="hljs-type">const</span> &amp;obj):<span class="hljs-built_in">node_value</span>(obj),<br><span class="hljs-built_in">p_left_tree</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>),<span class="hljs-built_in">p_right_tree</span>(<span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">/* Empty constructor */</span><br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br>Type Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;::<span class="hljs-built_in">value</span>() <span class="hljs-type">const</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> node_value;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br>Binary_node&lt;Type&gt; *Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;::<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>() <span class="hljs-type">const</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> p_left_tree;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br>Binary_node&lt;Type&gt; *Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;::<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>() <span class="hljs-type">const</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> p_right_tree;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;::<span class="hljs-built_in">is_leaf</span>() <span class="hljs-type">const</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>() == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) &amp;&amp; (<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>() == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>);<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;::<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>() <span class="hljs-type">const</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>() == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>() == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) ? <span class="hljs-number">1</span> : <span class="hljs-number">1</span> + <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>();<br>    &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">return</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>() == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) ? <span class="hljs-number">1</span> + <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>() :<br>        <span class="hljs-number">1</span> + <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>() + <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;::<span class="hljs-built_in">height</span>() <span class="hljs-type">const</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>() == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>() == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) ? <span class="hljs-number">0</span> : <span class="hljs-number">1</span> + <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">height</span>();<br>    &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">return</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>() == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) ? <span class="hljs-number">1</span> + <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">height</span>() :<br>                <span class="hljs-number">1</span> + <span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">height</span>(), <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">height</span>());<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br><span class="hljs-type">void</span> Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;::<span class="hljs-built_in">clear</span>(Binary_node *&amp;p_to_this) &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>() != <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">clear</span>(p_left_tree);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>() != <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>()-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">clear</span>(p_right_tree);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">delete</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span>;<br>    p_to_this = <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">preorder</span><span class="hljs-params">(Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;* root)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (root == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Empty subtree, do nothing */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">visit</span>(root); <span class="hljs-comment">/* Perform desired action */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">preorder</span>(root-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>());<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">preorder</span>(root-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>());<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">inorder</span><span class="hljs-params">(Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;* root)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (root == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Empty subtree, do nothing */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">inorder</span>(root-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>());<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">visit</span>(root); <span class="hljs-comment">/* Perform desired action */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">inorder</span>(root-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>());<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">typename</span> Type&gt;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">postorder</span><span class="hljs-params">(Binary_node&lt;Type&gt;* root)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (root == <span class="hljs-literal">nullptr</span>)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>; <span class="hljs-comment">/* Empty subtree, do nothing */</span><br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">postorder</span>(root-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">left</span>());<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">postorder</span>(root-&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">right</span>());<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">visit</span>(root); <span class="hljs-comment">/* Perform desired action */</span><br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li>LCRS：左儿子-右兄弟树。将一棵普通树转化为 LCRS 的算法称为 Knuth Transform<br>  <img src="/review/KnuthTransform.png"></li></ul></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    
